data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER HAS JUST REDUCED PRICE $25,000! Surrounded by mature landscaping, and oozing charm and curb appeal, you'll love this home from the moment you pull up. Beautifully decorated in neutral colors, the front room is currently being used as a dining room, but could easily be a home office or formal living room. Beautiful, open kitchen with breakfast bar seating, dining area, and living room all enjoy spectacular views of the pool and the lush preserve, and plenty of areas for swimming, dining, and relaxing! Large master suite with lots of closet space, beautiful master bath, built-in cabinets and counter space in the hall currently used as a bar and wine area off the kitchen and main living area. Laundry room, oversize two-car garage, three additional bedrooms and two bathrooms add to the convenience. There's even lots of storage under the staircase, as well as an open area for computer, workstation, or closet. Truly one of a kind, on a premium lot in a very central location near shopping, dining, entertainment, and the beaches. Live the Florida lifestyle to the fullest here.
